    <briefdescription>
<para>The native base class for the content widget representing a leaf-type setting category (contains setting entries). </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The native base class for the content widget representing a leaf-type setting category (contains setting entries). This is a subclass of <ref refid="classUSFCategoryTabBase" kindref="compound">USFCategoryTabBase</ref>. It is added to <ref refid="classUSFSettingsScreen" kindref="compound">USFSettingsScreen</ref>&apos;s TabContentSwitcher for leaf-type categories.</para>
<para>The widget blueprint implementing this class should be assigned to the LeafTabContentClass in the Developer Settings at Project Settings &gt; Plugins &gt; SettingsFramework. <simplesect kind="note"><para><computeroutput>Abstract</computeroutput> <computeroutput>BlueprintType</computeroutput> <computeroutput>Blueprintable</computeroutput> </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
